dc_title_s: Shinsen dōban Kyōto ichiran no zu; chosha Monji Tominosuke.; Kyōto ichiran no zu
dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Copperplate print. Oriented with north to the left. Relief and points of interest shown pictorially. Includes distance chart and legend. 1 map: col.; 34 x 47 cm., folded in covers 17 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
